land.localAuthorityCode.error.required                                              = Enter the local authority code
land.localAuthorityCode.error.length                                                = The local authority code must be 4 characters
land.localAuthorityCode.error.invalidChars                                          = The local authority code must only include numbers 0 to 9
land.localAuthorityCode.error.invalidFormat                                         = Enter a valid local authority code, like 0114 or 3935
land.localAuthorityCode.error.invalidArea                                           = Enter a valid local authority code for England or Northern Ireland
land.localAuthorityCode.error.invalidAreaPostcode                                   = Enter a valid local authority code that matches your postcode in England or Northern Ireland
land.localAuthorityCode.error.welsh                                                 = Welsh local authority codes are no longer recognised by SDLT when the effective date of the transaction is the same as or after 1 April 2018
