land.localAuthorityCode.regexExp                                                    = Invalid local authority code
land.localAuthorityCode.constraint.invalid                                          = Enter a valid local authority code for England or Northern Ireland

land.nlpgUprn.title                                                                 = What is the NLPG UPRN for the land or property? - About the land
land.nlpgUprn.heading                                                               = What is the NLPG UPRN for the land or property?
land.nlpgUprn.hint                                                                  = This number can be up to 12 digits, like 100023336956. You can find it using the FindMyAddress website (England) or the Pointer database (Northern Ireland).
