land.nlpgUprn.error.format                                                          = The NLPG UPRN must only include numbers 0 to 9
land.nlpgUprn.error.invalidFormat                                                   = Enter the NLPG UPRN in the correct format

land.landMineralsOrMineralRights.title                                              = Minerals or mineral rights
land.landMineralsOrMineralRights.heading                                            = Minerals or mineral rights
land.landMineralsOrMineralRights.subheading                                         = Are there any minerals or mineral rights reserved or excluded for the land or property?
land.landMineralsOrMineralRights.p                                                  = Mineral rights are the legal entitlement to exploit, mine or produce minerals and other natural resources beneath the land or property. When mineral rights are reserved or excluded, the owner of the land or property has no claim to any minerals or other natural resources beneath the land.
land.landMineralsOrMineralRights.checkYourAnswersLabel                              = Minerals or mineral rights reserved or excluded?
land.landMineralsOrMineralRights.error.required                                     = Select yes if there are minerals or mineral rights reserved or excluded for the land or property
land.landMineralsOrMineralRights.change.hidden                                      = Minerals or mineral rights reserved or excluded?

