transaction.beforeStart.title                                                       = Before you start - About the transaction
transaction.beforeStart.p1                                                          = In this section, you need to tell us about the transaction.
transaction.beforeStart.p2                                                          = We will ask for:
transaction.beforeStart.bullet1                                                     = the type of transaction
transaction.beforeStart.bullet2                                                     = the effective date of the transaction
transaction.beforeStart.bullet3                                                     = the total consideration in money or money’s worth
transaction.beforeStart.bullet4                                                     = the forms of consideration
transaction.beforeStart.bullet5                                                     = any considerations affected by uncertain future events
transaction.beforeStart.bullet6                                                     = whether the transaction is pursuant to a previous option agreement
transaction.beforeStart.p3                                                          = You can also provide:
transaction.beforeStart.bullet7                                                     = the date of contract or conclusion of missives
transaction.beforeStart.bullet8                                                     = the amount of VAT included in the total consideration
transaction.beforeStart.bullet9                                                     = if this transaction is linked to another
transaction.beforeStart.bullet10                                                    = the total consideration of all linked transactions
transaction.beforeStart.bullet11                                                    = the purchaser’s eligibility and reason for claiming relief
transaction.beforeStart.bullet12                                                    = how much partial relief the purchaser is claiming
transaction.beforeStart.bullet13                                                    = whether the purchaser is applying for a deferment
transaction.beforeStart.bullet14                                                    = how the land or property will be used
transaction.beforeStart.bullet15                                                    = the details and total consideration if the transaction is part of the sale of a business
transaction.beforeStart.bullet16                                                    = whether a CAP1 or NSBC application has been made and followed
transaction.beforeStart.bullet17                                                    = any restrictions, covenants or conditions affecting the transaction
transaction.beforeStart.bullet18                                                    = the address of any land or property being exchanged or part exchanged

transaction.typeOfTransaction.title                                                 = What type of transaction is this?
transaction.typeOfTransaction.heading                                               = What type of transaction is this?
transaction.typeOfTransaction.checkYourAnswersLabel                                 = What type of transaction is this?
transaction.typeOfTransaction.error.required                                        = Select the type of transaction

transaction.transactionEffectiveDate.title                                          = Effective date of the transaction - About the transaction
transaction.transactionEffectiveDate.heading                                        = Effective date of the transaction
transaction.transactionEffectiveDate.subheading                                     = What is the effective date of the transaction?
transaction.transactionEffectiveDate.details.summary                                = About substantial performance
transaction.transactionEffectiveDate.details.content                                = The effective date of transaction can be brought forward if the contract is substantially performed prior to completion. Substantial performance occurs when the purchaser pays 90% or more of the total price, occupies 90% or more of the property, or pays any rent.
transaction.transactionEffectiveDate.p                                              = This is typically the date when the transaction is legally completed. This means the land or property has changed ownership and the purchaser becomes liable to pay SDLT.
transaction.transactionEffectiveDate.hint                                           = For example, 27 3 2023
transaction.transactionEffectiveDate.checkYourAnswersLabel                          = Effective date of transaction
transaction.transactionEffectiveDate.error.required.all                             = Enter the effective date of the transaction
transaction.transactionEffectiveDate.error.required.two                             = The effective date of transaction must include {0} and {1}
transaction.transactionEffectiveDate.error.required                                 = The effective date of the transaction must include a {0}
transaction.transactionEffectiveDate.error.invalid                                  = The effective date of the transaction must be a real date
transaction.transactionEffectiveDate.change.hidden                                  = Effective date of transaction
transaction.transactionEffectiveDate.error.date.range.min                           = The effective date of transaction must be the same as or after 1 11 2003
transaction.transactionEffectiveDate.error.date.range.max                           = The effective date of the transaction cannot be in the future
transaction.transactionEffectiveDate.missing                                        = Provide Effective Date

transaction.confirmTypeOfTransaction.title                                          = Confirm the type of transaction - About the transaction
transaction.confirmTypeOfTransaction.heading                                        = Confirm the type of transaction
transaction.confirmTypeOfTransaction.subHeading                                     = Is this the correct type of transaction?
transaction.confirmTypeOfTransaction.p                                              = This was your answer when creating this return.
transaction.confirmTypeOfTransaction.error.required                                 = Select Yes or No
transaction.confirmTypeOfTransaction.change.hidden                                  = Confirm the type of transaction

transaction.changeTypeOfTransaction.title                                           = Changing the type of transaction - About the transaction
transaction.changeTypeOfTransaction.heading                                         = Changing the transaction type
transaction.changeTypeOfTransaction.subHeading                                      = Are you sure you need to change the transaction type?
transaction.changeTypeOfTransaction.hint.option1                                    = By changing the type of transaction, the amount of SDLT due may change. All information about the lease will be deleted from this return.
transaction.changeTypeOfTransaction.hint.option2                                    = By changing the type of transaction, the amount of SDLT due may change. All information about the total consideration of the transaction will be deleted from this return.
transaction.changeTypeOfTransaction.hint.option3                                    = By changing the type of transaction, the amount of SDLT due may change. All information about the total premium payable and the net present value will be deleted from this return. You will now need to enter all information about the total consideration of the transaction.
transaction.changeTypeOfTransaction.hint.option4                                    = By changing the type of transaction, the amount of SDLT due may change. All information you have entered about the total consideration of the transaction will be deleted. You will now need to enter the total premium payable and the net present value.
transaction.changeTypeOfTransaction.checkYourAnswersLabel                           = Changing the transaction type
transaction.changeTypeOfTransaction.error.required                                  = Select yes if you need to change the transaction type
transaction.changeTypeOfTransaction.change.hidden                                   = Changing the transaction type
transaction.changeTypeOfTransaction.missing                                         = Select yes or no


transaction.addDateOfContract.title                                                 = Date of contract
transaction.addDateOfContract.heading                                               = Date of contract
transaction.addDateOfContract.h2                                                    = Do you know the date of contract or conclusion of missives?
transaction.addDateOfContract.p1                                                    = The date of contract (or conclusion of missives) is when the agreement of sale becomes a binding contract between the purchaser and vendor, usually through the exchange of contracts. Typically, this is not the same day as the effective date of transaction.
transaction.addDateOfContract.checkYourAnswersLabel                                 = Contract or conclusion of missives
transaction.addDateOfContract.error.required                                        = Select yes if you know the date of contract or conclusion of missives
transaction.addDateOfContract.change.hidden                                         = Contract or conclusion of missives
transaction.addDateOfContract.missing                                               = Select if you know the date of contract or conclusion of missives

transaction.linkedTransactions.title                                                = Linked transactions
transaction.linkedTransactions.heading                                              = Linked transactions
transaction.linkedTransactions.h2                                                   = Is this transaction linked to another?
transaction.linkedTransactions.p1                                                   = A transaction is linked when it forms part of an arrangement, scheme or series of transactions between the same vendor and purchaser or connected persons.
transaction.linkedTransactions.checkYourAnswersLabel                                = Is this transaction linked to another?
transaction.linkedTransactions.error.required                                       = Select yes if this transaction is linked to another
transaction.linkedTransactions.change.hidden                                        = Is this transaction linked to another?
transaction.linkedTransactions.missing                                              = Select if this transaction is linked to another

transaction.transactionVatIncluded.title                                            = Is VAT included in the total consideration?
transaction.transactionVatIncluded.heading                                          = Is VAT included in the total consideration?
transaction.transactionVatIncluded.checkYourAnswersLabel                            = Is VAT included in the total consideration?
transaction.transactionVatIncluded.error.required                                   = Select yes if VAT is included in the total consideration
transaction.transactionVatIncluded.change.hidden                                    = Is VAT included in the total consideration?
transaction.transactionVatIncluded.hint                                             = Any VAT payable on the transaction must be included in the total consideration for SDLT purposes
transaction.transactionVatIncluded.missing                                          = Please select if VAT is included in the total consideration

transaction.transactionDateOfContract.title                                         = What is the date of contract or conclusion of missives?
transaction.transactionDateOfContract.heading                                       = What is the date of contract or conclusion of missives?
transaction.transactionDateOfContract.hint                                          = For example, 27 3 2023
transaction.transactionDateOfContract.checkYourAnswersLabel                         = Date of contract or conclusion of missives
transaction.transactionDateOfContract.error.required.all                            = Enter the date of contract
transaction.transactionDateOfContract.error.required.two                            = The date of contract must include {0} and {1}
transaction.transactionDateOfContract.error.required                                = The date of contract must include {0}
transaction.transactionDateOfContract.error.invalid                                 = The date of contract must be a real date
transaction.transactionDateOfContract.change.hidden                                 = Date of contract or conclusion of missives
transaction.transactionDateOfContract.error.date.range.min                          = The date of contract must be the same as or after 01 01 1900
transaction.transactionDateOfContract.error.date.range.max                          = The date of contract cannot be in the future

transaction.totalConsiderationOfTransaction.title                                   = Total consideration of the transaction
transaction.totalConsiderationOfTransaction.heading                                 = Total consideration of the transaction
transaction.totalConsiderationOfTransaction.p1                                      = This is typically the purchase price of the land or property in pounds sterling. The total consideration can also refer to anything of value (money’s worth) given by the purchaser as part of the transaction, including:
transaction.totalConsiderationOfTransaction.li1                                     = the release or assumption of a debt
transaction.totalConsiderationOfTransaction.li2                                     = goods and services
transaction.totalConsiderationOfTransaction.li3                                     = the transfer of other property
transaction.totalConsiderationOfTransaction.li4                                     = payment of the vendor’s legal costs
transaction.totalConsiderationOfTransaction.h2                                      = What is the total consideration in money or money’s worth?
transaction.totalConsiderationOfTransaction.hint                                    = Enter the value in whole pounds only, for example £200,000
transaction.totalConsiderationOfTransaction.checkYourAnswersLabel                   = Total consideration of the transaction
transaction.totalConsiderationOfTransaction.error.required                          = Enter the total consideration in money or money’s worth, in pounds
transaction.totalConsiderationOfTransaction.error.invalidNumeric                    = The total consideration in money or money’s worth must only include commas and numbers 0 to 9
transaction.totalConsiderationOfTransaction.error.invalidWholeNumber                = Enter the total consideration in money or money’s worth in whole pounds
transaction.totalConsiderationOfTransaction.error.maximum                           = The total consideration in money or money’s worth must be equal to or less than £9,999,999,999
transaction.totalConsiderationOfTransaction.error.vatIncludedInTotalConsideration   = The total consideration in money or money’s worth must be more than the amount of VAT included in the total consideration
transaction.totalConsiderationOfTransaction.error.totalConsideration                = The total consideration in money or money’s worth must be less than the total consideration of all linked transactions
transaction.totalConsiderationOfTransaction.change.hidden                           = Total consideration of the transaction
transaction.totalConsiderationOfTransaction.missing                                 = Enter the total consideration in money or money’s worth

transaction.vatAmount.title                                                         = Amount of VAT
transaction.vatAmount.heading                                                       = Amount of VAT
transaction.vatAmount.p1                                                            = The total consideration must reflect VAT rates on the effective date of transaction. Any subsequent changes do not affect the amount due.
transaction.vatAmount.h2                                                            = What is the amount of VAT included in the total consideration?
transaction.vatAmount.hint                                                          = Enter the value in whole pounds only, for example £200,000
transaction.vatAmount.checkYourAnswersLabel                                         = Amount of VAT included in the total consideration
transaction.vatAmount.error.required                                                = Enter the amount of VAT included in the total consideration, in pounds
transaction.vatAmount.error.invalidNumeric                                          = The amount of VAT included in the total consideration must only include numbers 0 to 9 and commas
transaction.vatAmount.error.invalidWholeNumber                                      = Enter the amount of VAT included in the total consideration in whole pounds
transaction.vatAmount.error.maximum                                                 = The amount of VAT included in the total consideration must be equal to or less than £9,999,999,999
transaction.vatAmount.error.vatIncludedInTotalConsideration                         = The amount of VAT included in the total consideration must be less than the total consideration in money or money’s worth
transaction.vatAmount.change.hidden                                                 = Amount of VAT included in the total consideration
transaction.vatAmount.missing                                                       = Enter the amount of VAT included in the total consideration

transaction.transactionFormsOfConsideration.title                                   = Forms of consideration
transaction.transactionFormsOfConsideration.heading                                 = Forms of consideration
transaction.transactionFormsOfConsideration.p1                                      = There are different forms of consideration. Most transactions are paid in pounds sterling, but if other types of consideration are involved in this transaction, you need to declare them. All considerations must be valued at their full market value on the effective date of transaction.
transaction.transactionFormsOfConsideration.subHeading                              = What form does the consideration take?
transaction.transactionFormsOfConsideration.hint                                    = Select up to 4 considerations
transaction.transactionFormsOfConsideration.cash                                    = Cash
transaction.transactionFormsOfConsideration.debt                                    = Debt
transaction.transactionFormsOfConsideration.debt.hintText                           = Including assumption by the purchaser of outstanding mortgage
transaction.transactionFormsOfConsideration.buildingWorks                           = Building works
transaction.transactionFormsOfConsideration.employment                              = Employment
transaction.transactionFormsOfConsideration.employment.hintText                     = Special rules might apply if the vendor is the purchaser’s employee
transaction.transactionFormsOfConsideration.other                                   = Other
transaction.transactionFormsOfConsideration.other.hintText                          = Such as an annuity
transaction.transactionFormsOfConsideration.sharesInAQuotedCompany                  = Shares in a quoted company
transaction.transactionFormsOfConsideration.sharesInAnUnquotedCompany               = Shares in an unquoted company
transaction.transactionFormsOfConsideration.otherLand                               = Other land
transaction.transactionFormsOfConsideration.services                                = Services
transaction.transactionFormsOfConsideration.contingent                              = Contingent
transaction.transactionFormsOfConsideration.checkYourAnswersLabel                   = Forms of consideration
transaction.transactionFormsOfConsideration.error.required                          = Select up to 4 considerations
transaction.transactionFormsOfConsideration.change.hidden                           = Forms of consideration
transaction.transactionFormsOfConsideration.missing                                 = Select forms of consideration

transaction.addRegisteredCharityNumber.title                                        = Registered charity number - About the transaction
transaction.addRegisteredCharityNumber.heading                                      = Registered charity number
transaction.addRegisteredCharityNumber.subheading                                   = Do you know the charity’s registered number?
transaction.addRegisteredCharityNumber.p1                                           = A charity’s registered number is a unique identifier that validates they are regulated and legitimate. You can find a charity’s registered number through the Charity Commission.
transaction.addRegisteredCharityNumber.p2                                           = For England & Wales, visit <a href="{0}" class="govuk-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">{1}</a>.
transaction.addRegisteredCharityNumber.p2.suffix                                    = the Charity Commission at GOV.UK (opens in new tab)
transaction.addRegisteredCharityNumber.p2.link                                      = https://register-of-charities.charitycommission.gov.uk/en/
transaction.addRegisteredCharityNumber.p3                                           = For Northern Ireland, visit <a href="{0}" class="govuk-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">{1}</a>.
transaction.addRegisteredCharityNumber.p3.suffix                                    = the Charity Commission for Northern Ireland (opens in new tab)
transaction.addRegisteredCharityNumber.p3.link                                      = https://www.charitycommissionni.org.uk/charity-search/?pageNumber=1
transaction.addRegisteredCharityNumber.checkYourAnswersLabel                        = Do you know the charity’s registered number?
transaction.addRegisteredCharityNumber.error.required                               = Select yes if you know the charity’s registered number
transaction.addRegisteredCharityNumber.change.hidden                                = Do you know the charity’s registered number?
transaction.addRegisteredCharityNumber.missing                                      = Select registered charity number

