transaction.totalConsiderationOfLinkedTransaction.title                             = Total consideration of all linked transactions
transaction.totalConsiderationOfLinkedTransaction.heading                           = Total consideration of all linked transactions
transaction.totalConsiderationOfLinkedTransaction.p1                                = When two or more transactions are linked, SDLT is calculated on the aggregate total consideration. You must include any payable VAT for all linked transactions, and anything of value (money’s worth) given by the purchaser as part of the transaction, like the release or assumption of a debt.
transaction.totalConsiderationOfLinkedTransaction.h2                                = What is the total consideration in money or money’s worth of all transactions?
transaction.totalConsiderationOfLinkedTransaction.hint                              = Enter the value in whole pounds only, for example £200,000
transaction.totalConsiderationOfLinkedTransaction.checkYourAnswersLabel             = Total consideration of all linked transactions
transaction.totalConsiderationOfLinkedTransaction.error.required                    = Enter the total consideration in money or money’s worth of all transactions, in pounds
transaction.totalConsiderationOfLinkedTransaction.error.invalidNumeric              = The total consideration in money or money’s worth of all transactions must only include numbers 0 to 9 and commas
transaction.totalConsiderationOfLinkedTransaction.error.invalidWholeNumber          = Enter the total consideration in money or money’s worth of all transactions in whole pounds
transaction.totalConsiderationOfLinkedTransaction.error.maximum                     = The total consideration in money or money’s worth must be less than £9,999,999,999
transaction.totalConsiderationOfLinkedTransaction.error.totalConsideration          = The total consideration in money or money’s worth of all transactions must be more than the total consideration of a single transaction
transaction.totalConsiderationOfLinkedTransaction.change.hidden                     = Total consideration of all linked transactions
transaction.totalConsiderationOfLinkedTransaction.missing                           = Enter the total consideration of all linked transactions

transaction.purchaserEligibleToClaimRelief.title                                    = Claiming relief
transaction.purchaserEligibleToClaimRelief.heading                                  = Claiming relief
transaction.purchaserEligibleToClaimRelief.p1                                       = Relief means any reduction or exemption to the amount of payable SDLT, based on specific circumstances or criteria, like First Time Buyers’ Relief.
transaction.purchaserEligibleToClaimRelief.h2                                       = Is the purchaser eligible to claim relief?
transaction.purchaserEligibleToClaimRelief.checkYourAnswersLabel                    = Is the purchaser eligible to claim relief?
transaction.purchaserEligibleToClaimRelief.error.required                           = Select yes if the purchaser is eligible to claim relief
transaction.purchaserEligibleToClaimRelief.change.hidden                            = Is the purchaser eligible to claim relief?
transaction.purchaserEligibleToClaimRelief.change.missing                           = Select if purchaser is eligible to claim relief

transaction.transactionPartialRelief.title                                          = Partial relief
transaction.transactionPartialRelief.heading                                        = Partial relief
transaction.transactionPartialRelief.subheading                                     = Is the purchaser claiming relief on part of the land or property?
transaction.transactionPartialRelief.p                                              = Partial relief is available when a transaction meets most, but not all, conditions for full relief, like Freeport or Investment Zone Relief. This is where the land or property is partially located within a designated tax site, meaning a purchaser would only claim relief for the qualifying part.
transaction.transactionPartialRelief.checkYourAnswersLabel                          = Is the purchaser claiming relief on part of the land or property?
transaction.transactionPartialRelief.error.required                                 = Select yes if the purchaser is claiming relief on part of the land or property
transaction.transactionPartialRelief.change.hidden                                  = Is the purchaser claiming relief on part of the land or property?
transaction.transactionPartialRelief.missing                                        = Select if the purchaser is claiming relief on part of the land or property

transaction.claimingPartialReliefAmount.title                                       = Claiming partial relief
transaction.claimingPartialReliefAmount.heading                                     = Claiming partial relief
transaction.claimingPartialReliefAmount.p1                                          = When claiming relief on part of the land or property, only enter the amount that remains chargeable to SDLT.
transaction.claimingPartialReliefAmount.h2                                          = How much relief is being claimed on part of the land or property?
transaction.claimingPartialReliefAmount.hint                                        = Enter the value in whole pounds only, for example £200,000
transaction.claimingPartialReliefAmount.checkYourAnswersLabel                       = Amount of partial relief being claimed
transaction.claimingPartialReliefAmount.error.required                              = Enter the amount of relief being claimed on part of the land or property, in pounds
transaction.claimingPartialReliefAmount.error.invalidNumeric                        = The amount of relief being claimed on part of the land or property must only include numbers 0 to 9 and commas
transaction.claimingPartialReliefAmount.error.invalidWholeNumber                    = Enter the amount of relief being claimed on part of the land or property in whole pounds
transaction.claimingPartialReliefAmount.error.maximum                               = The amount of relief being claimed on part of the land or property must be equal to or less than £9,999,999,999
transaction.claimingPartialReliefAmount.change.hidden                               = Amount of partial relief being claimed
transaction.claimingPartialReliefAmount.missing                                     = Enter the amount of relief being claimed on part of the land or property

