taxCalculation.confirm.effectiveDateOfTransaction.p1                                = Before completing the tax calculation, you must confirm the effective date of the transaction. Changing this date may affect the amount of SDLT due and require you to update earlier answers in this return.
taxCalculation.confirm.effectiveDateOfTransaction.p2                                = Do not complete this section if the effective date is subject to change or awaiting confirmation from the purchaser.

