transaction.deferringPayment.title                                                  = Deferring payment
transaction.deferringPayment.heading                                                = Deferring payment
transaction.deferringPayment.p1                                                     = SDLT payment may be deferred when the whole or part of the chargeable consideration:
transaction.deferringPayment.li1                                                    = is uncertain or contingent on future events, like obtaining planning permission
transaction.deferringPayment.li2                                                    = becomes payable, or may become payable, more than six months after the effective date of transaction
transaction.deferringPayment.h2                                                     = Is the purchaser applying for a deferment?
transaction.deferringPayment.checkYourAnswersLabel                                  = Is the purchaser applying for a deferment?
transaction.deferringPayment.error.required                                         = Select yes if the purchaser is applying for a deferment
transaction.deferringPayment.change.hidden                                          = Is the purchaser applying for a deferment?

transaction.transactionUseOfLandOrProperty.title                                    = The use of the land or property
transaction.transactionUseOfLandOrProperty.heading                                  = The use of the land or property
transaction.transactionUseOfLandOrProperty.subheading                               = What is the land or property to be used for?
transaction.transactionUseOfLandOrProperty.p1                                       = Non-residential property is defined by exclusion, which means any land or property that does not meet the specific definition of residential property.
transaction.transactionUseOfLandOrProperty.p2                                       = As a non-residential property, the classification for this return depends on the actual use, or suitability for use, on the effective date of the transaction.
transaction.transactionUseOfLandOrProperty.office                                   = Office
transaction.transactionUseOfLandOrProperty.hotel                                    = Hotel
transaction.transactionUseOfLandOrProperty.shop                                     = Shop
transaction.transactionUseOfLandOrProperty.warehouse                                = Warehouse
transaction.transactionUseOfLandOrProperty.factory                                  = Factory
transaction.transactionUseOfLandOrProperty.otherIndustrialUnit                      = Other industrial unit
transaction.transactionUseOfLandOrProperty.other                                    = Other
transaction.transactionUseOfLandOrProperty.error.required                           = Select at least one use for the land or property
transaction.transactionUseOfLandOrProperty.change.hidden                            = How the land or property will be used
transaction.transactionUseOfLandOrProperty.hint                                     = Select all that apply
transaction.transactionUseOfLandOrProperty.checkYourAnswersLabel                    = How the land or property will be used
transaction.transactionUseOfLandOrProperty.missing                                  = Select how the land or property will be used

transaction.considerationsAffectedUncertain.title                                   = Considerations affected by uncertain future events - About the transaction
transaction.considerationsAffectedUncertain.heading                                 = Considerations affected by uncertain future events
transaction.considerationsAffectedUncertain.subHeading                              = Is any part of the consideration contingent or dependent on uncertain future events?
transaction.considerationsAffectedUncertain.error.required                          = Select yes if any part of the consideration is contingent or dependent on uncertain future events
transaction.considerationsAffectedUncertain.p1                                      = This means any SDLT payment that may be influenced by something yet to happen, like projected company profits or receiving planning permission.
transaction.considerationsAffectedUncertain.p2                                      = Uncertain future events are typically defined as:
transaction.considerationsAffectedUncertain.bullet1                                 = a contingent consideration, where a fixed sum is only paid, or not paid, when the uncertain future event occurs
transaction.considerationsAffectedUncertain.bullet2                                 = a dependent consideration, where the amount or value of a consideration depends on the uncertain future event
transaction.considerationsAffectedUncertain.checkYourAnswersLabel                   = Is any part of the consideration contingent or dependent on uncertain future events?
transaction.considerationsAffectedUncertain.change.hidden                           = Is any part of the consideration contingent or dependent on uncertain future events?

