transaction.descriptionOfRestrictions.heading                                       = What are the restrictions, covenants or conditions affecting the value of the interest transferred or granted?
transaction.descriptionOfRestrictions.subHeading                                    = Have you applied for a CAP1 or NSBC in relation to this transaction?
transaction.descriptionOfRestrictions.hint                                          = Provide a brief description, like a vendor’s right to buy back at less than market value
transaction.descriptionOfRestrictions.error.required                                = Enter a brief description of the restrictions, covenants or conditions affecting the value of the interest transferred or granted
transaction.descriptionOfRestrictions.error.regex                                   = The brief description of the restrictions, covenants or conditions must only include letters a to z, numbers 0 to 9, spaces and full stops
transaction.descriptionOfRestrictions.error.length                                  = The brief description of the restrictions, covenants or conditions must be 42 characters or fewer
transaction.descriptionOfRestrictions.checkYourAnswersLabel                         = What are the restrictions, covenants or conditions?
transaction.descriptionOfRestrictions.change.hidden                                 = What are the restrictions, covenants or conditions?

transaction.transactionExercisingAnOption.title                                     = Exercising an option
transaction.transactionExercisingAnOption.heading                                   = Exercising an option
transaction.transactionExercisingAnOption.p                                         = This is when the transaction is the result of an option being exercised. The grant of an option and the subsequent purchase of the land or property are typically linked but considered two separate transactions.
transaction.transactionExercisingAnOption.subheading                                = Is this transaction pursuant to a previous option agreement?
transaction.transactionExercisingAnOption.checkYourAnswersLabel                     = Transaction pursuant to a previous option agreement?
transaction.transactionExercisingAnOption.error.required                            = Select yes if this transaction is pursuant to a previous option agreement
transaction.transactionExercisingAnOption.change.hidden                             = Transaction pursuant to a previous option agreement?

lease.beforeYouStart.p1                                                             = In this section, you need to tell us about the lease on the land or property.
lease.beforeYouStart.p2                                                             = We will ask for:
lease.beforeYouStart.l1.li1                                                         = the type of lease
lease.beforeYouStart.l1.li2                                                         = the lease start date
lease.beforeYouStart.l1.li3                                                         = the lease end date
lease.beforeYouStart.l1.li4                                                         = any rent-free period included in the lease
lease.beforeYouStart.l1.li5                                                         = the annual starting rent
lease.beforeYouStart.l1.li6                                                         = the end date for annual starting rent
lease.beforeYouStart.l1.li7                                                         = the later rent if known
lease.beforeYouStart.l1.li8                                                         = whether the later rent is more than £1,000
lease.beforeYouStart.l1.li9                                                         = the net present value (NPV)
lease.beforeYouStart.p3                                                             = You can also provide:
lease.beforeYouStart.l2.li1                                                         = the duration of the rent-free period
lease.beforeYouStart.l2.li2                                                         = the total amount of VAT on the annual rent
lease.beforeYouStart.l2.li3                                                         = the total premium payable including VAT

