crossflow.land.Cf-14.body                                                           = This local authority code cannot be used when the date of contract is the same as or after 1 April 2015.
crossflow.land.Cf-15.body                                                           = This local authority code is no longer recognised by SDLT when the effective date of the transaction is the same as or after 1 April 2015.
crossflow.land.Cf-16.body                                                           = Areas of land or properties with a Scottish postcode are no longer recognised by SDLT when the effective date of the transaction is the same as or after 1 April 2015.

crossflow.land.Cf-8.inline                                                          = Entering this local authority code means the effective date of the transaction must be before 1 April 2018
