crossflow.land.cta.enterDifferentCode                                               = Enter a different local authority code.
crossflow.land.cta.enterDifferentPostcode                                           = Enter a different postcode.



crossflow.lease.section                                                             = About the lease
crossflow.lease.heading                                                             = Update the type of lease
crossflow.lease.Cf-5a.body                                                          = The type of lease must match the type of property. The type of lease must be ‘R - Residential’ when the type of property is either:
crossflow.lease.Cf-5a.bullet1                                                       = ‘01 - Residential’
crossflow.lease.Cf-5a.bullet2                                                       = ‘04 - Additional residential property liable to higher rate’
crossflow.lease.cta.changeLeaseType                                                 = Select ‘R - Residential’ as the type of lease.
crossflow.lease.Cf-5a.inline                                                        = When the type of lease is ‘R - Residential’, the type of property must be ‘01 - Residential’ or ‘04 - Additional residential property liable to higher rate’
crossflow.lease.Cf-5b.body                                                          = The type of lease must match the type of property. When the type of property is ‘02 - Mixed’, the type of lease must be ‘M - Mixed use’.
crossflow.lease.Cf-5b.inline                                                        = When the type of lease is ‘M - Mixed use’, the type of property must be ‘02 - Mixed’
crossflow.lease.Cf-5c.body                                                          = The type of lease must match the type of property. When the type of property is ‘03 - Non-residential’, the type of lease must be ‘N - Non-residential’.
crossflow.lease.Cf-5c.inline                                                        = When the type of lease is ‘N - Non-residential’, the type of property must be ‘03 - Non-residential’

crossflow.land.Cf-6.heading                                                         = There is a problem
crossflow.land.Cf-6.body                                                            = Multiple areas of land or properties with lease involvement must share the same property type.
crossflow.land.Cf-6.p2                                                              = Review the property type for all the interests listed and select either:
crossflow.land.Cf-6.bullet1                                                         = the same property type for all interests
crossflow.land.Cf-6.bullet2                                                         = ‘02 - Mixed’ if there are different property types
crossflow.land.Cf-6.inline                                                          = Areas of land or property with lease involvement must share the same property type. If there are multiple property types, select ‘02 - Mixed’ for all areas of land or property added

crossflow.land.Cf-6.column.land                                                     = Land
crossflow.land.Cf-6.column.propertyType                                             = Type of property
crossflow.land.Cf-6.column.actions                                                  = Actions

crossflow.lease.Cf-5a.cta                                                           = Select ‘R - Residential’ as the type of lease.
crossflow.lease.Cf-5b.cta                                                           = Select ‘M - Mixed use’ as the type of lease.
crossflow.lease.Cf-5c.cta                                                           = Select ‘N - Non-residential’ as the type of lease.

